<h2>Harvesting</h2>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>URL to harvest Marc XML:</strong>
    <span>http://HOST:PORT/records/BIB_ID/create?format=marc21</span>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>URL to harvest structural XML:</strong>
    <span>http://HOST:PORT/records/BIB_ID/create?format=structural&amp;image_id_prefix=IMAGE_ID_PREFIX</span>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>URL to harvest OPenn-compliant XML (second argument optional)</strong>
    <span>http://HOST:PORT/records/BIB_ID/create?format=openn&amp;image_id_prefix=IMAGE_ID_PREFIX</span>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>URL to construct/harvest IIIF presentation manifest for a Colenda repository</strong>
    <span>http://HOST:PORT/records/REPO_ID/create?format=iiif_presentation</span>
  </li>
</ul>

<h2>Display</h2>
<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>URL to display XML:</strong>
    <span>http://HOST:PORT/records/ID/show?format=FORMAT</span>
  </li>
</ul>

